HEADWORD: Hodr
<hw>Hodr</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A blind god; misled
by Loki he kills Balder by throwing a bough of mistletoe.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Hoth, Hothr, Hoder.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

